the Tanzanian police showed that the bomb explosion happened at the
U.S. embassy here Friday morning was planted on an oil tanker
belonging to the embassy.
</P>
<P>
The bomb blast killed at least seven and wounded more than 50
Tanzanians at the embassy.
</P>
<P>
A spokesman for the police told a press conference in the
evening that the bomb exploded while the tanker was entering the
main entrance of the embassy in downtown Dar es Salaam.
</P>
