issue and has intensified security at all vital installations in
the city including surroundings of the embassy.
</P>
<P>
Mwansasu said that heads of defence and security organs have
formed a joint five-man task force which was led by the Director
of Criminal Investigation Adadi Rajabu and will make a close
followup on the issue, but so far no one has been arrested in
connection with the incident.
</P>
<P>
The Commissioner appealled to the people to volunteer
information on any person they suspected to have caused the
explosion.
</P>
