embassy in Dar-es-Salaam killed three Tanzanian guards and two
locally-hired embassy staff. There have been no reports of
casualties of Americans there.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. Air Force is sending at least two military aircraft
with a surgical team and medical evacuation personnel to Kenya
and Tanzania, a Defense Department spokeswoman said.
</P>
