<P>
TEHRAN -- Iranian Foreign Minister Kamal Kharrazi has voiced
Tehran's strong opposition to any foreign military intervention
in its northeastern neighbor Afghanistan, the official news
agency IRNA reported on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
No country should intervene and waste its potentials and
