<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Down 33.2 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, August 8 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange market
tumbled Saturday, with the index losing 33.2 points, or 1.6
percent, to close down at 2,091.1 points.
</P>
<P>
A total of 64.74 million shares changed hands in 1,340 deals,
as against 68.50 million shares in 1,458 deals Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The turnover dropped from Wednesday's 13.87 million Kuwaiti
dinars (45.77 million U.S. dollars) to 12.04 million dinars (39.73
million dollars). 
</P>
