money or we would all be running exclusively for the Golden
League's one million dollars jackpot. This is about respect and
acknowledgment. We didn't feel either based on the terms they
offered us."
</P>
<P>
Greene recently defeated a world-class 100-meters field at the
Goodwill Games and training partner Boldon, the world 200-meters
champion, won the 200 meters there. 
