imposed by FIFA which had threatened to ban Poland's national
squad and club teams from international competition unless the
PZPN board sacked by Debski were reinstated.
</P>
<P>
The controversy was sparked in April when the PZPN refused to
let sports ministry inspectors investigate their financial records
for suspected irregularities.
</P>
