<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, August 24 (Xinhua) -- Two different boat
accidents in Lake Victoria and Lake Manyara in Tanzania have
killed at least 21 people, media reports said.
</P>
<P>
Eighteen passengers got drowned Friday in Lake Victoria after
their boat capsized in the Serengeti District, said the Mwanza
Regional Police Commander Eliah Kihengu.
</P>
<P>
