injured in the bomb attacks against the U.S. embassies in Kenya
and Tanzania.
</P>
<P>
Police said in Nairobi at least 74 were killed and 1,643 were
wounded. In the Tanzanian capital of Dar es Salaam, at least seven
were killed and 72 others were injured. 
