Two bombs exploded outside the U.S. embassies in Kenya and
Tanzania Friday. They killed at least 81 people and injuring more
than 1,700 others.
</P>
<P>
At least 74, including eight Americans, were killed in Nairobi,
the capital of Kenya, and more than 1,640 were wounded, while at
least seven were reported dead and 72 hurt in Dar es Salaam, the
