<HEADLINE> Yugoslavia, United States, Russia, Greece into Semis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, August 7 (Xinhua) -- Yugoslavia led other three
favorites to enter the semi-finals at the World Basketball
Championship on Friday.
</P>
<P>
Yugoslavia will be joined in the semi-finals by the United
States, Greece and Russia.
</P>
<P>
Yugoslavia, Greece and the American team all narrowly averted
upsets to scrape into the semi-finals. Russia was the only team
to advance with less trouble.
</P>
<P>
Yugoslavia was down seven points to Argentina but came back to
win 70-62. They will play hosts Greece in the semi-finals.
</P>
<P>
Greece held off Spain 69-62 after leading by just one point
with 2:30 remaining.
</P>
<P>
The American team trailed Italy for most time of the match but
rallied to edge Italy 80-77 to set up a semi-final meet with
Russia. Russia entered the semi-finals with a 82-67 victory over
Lithuania. 
</P>
