are admitted, said all the dead are Tanzanians, including five
men and two women.
</P>
<P>
One man was identified as Mtendeje Rajab, a 25-year-old man
who works as a security guard at the embassy.
</P>
<P>
Some of the people wept bitterly on seeing bodies of their
relatives removed from ambulances while others were running from
place to place at the hospital in search of their relatives.
