the injured have been sent by several ambulances to the
Muhimibili Medical Center, the country's largest hospital, for
medical treatment.
</P>
<P>
The explosion has also affected neighboring residents. A
security guard of the neighboring French embassy, and a
five-year-old Tanzanian child in the vicinity were also injured.
</P>
<P>
The office buildings and cars are in "bad shape," he said,
adding that the fire following the explosion, that could be heard
miles away, has been extinguished. 
